headline: VULCAN ANNOUNCES FIRST QUARTER 2025 CONFERENCE CALL
summary: Vulcan Materials Company (NYSE: VMC) will host its first quarter 2025 earnings conference call on Wednesday, April 30, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. CT (10:00 a.m. ET). Financial results will be released before the NYSE market opens.

headline: Strength Seen in Vulcan (VMC): Can Its 5.8% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Vulcan (VMC) saw its shares surge in the last session with trading volume being higher than average. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions may not translate into further price increase in the near term.
